quran[82]{c,v,t}:
  100,9,Kiya issay who waqat maloom nahi jabb qabron mein jo kuch hy nikal liya jaey ga
  100,10,Aur seenon ki poshida batein zahir kerdi jaeingi
  100,11,Be-shak inka rab uss din unkay haal say poora ba-khabar hoga
  101,1,Kharkhara deney wali
  101,2,Kiaya hy who kharkhara deney wali
  101,3,Tujhay kiya maloom kay who kharkhara deney wali kia hy
  101,4,Jiss din insan bikhray huye perwanon ki tarah hojaeyen gy
  101,5,Aur pahar dhunay huye rangeen oon ki tarah hojaein gay
  101,6,phir jiss kay palry bhari hongy
  101,7,Who to dilpasand aram ki zindagi mein hoga
  101,8,Aur jiss kay palry halky hongy
  101,9,uss ka thikana Laaviya hai
  101,10,Tujhy kia maloom kay yeh kiya hai
  101,11,woh Tand-o-tez aag (hai)
  102,1,Zeyadti ki chahat nay tumhein ghafil kerdia
  102,2,Yahan tak kay tum qabastan ja phunchy
  102,3,Hergiz nahi tum unqareeb maloom kerlogay
  102,4,Hergiz nahi phir tumhein jald ilm hojaey ga
  102,5,Hergiz nahi ager tum yaqeeni tor per jan lo
  102,6,To be-shak tum jahanum dekhlogay
  102,7,Aur tum ussy yaqeen ki aankh say dekhlogy
  102,8,Phir uss din tum say zarror bil-zaroor nematon ka sawal hoga
  103,1,Zamaney ki qasam
  103,2,Beyshak (bil-yaqeen)insane sir ta sir nuqsan mein hay
  103,3,Siwaey un logon kay jo eman laey aur nek amal kiey aur(jinhon nay)apas mein haq ki waseeyat ki aur aik doosry ko sabar ki naseehat ki
  104,1,Bari kharabi hai her aisy shaks ki jo aib tatolney wala geebat kerney wala ho
  104,2,Jo maal ko jama kerta jaey or ginta jaey
  104,3,Woh samjhta hy kay uska maal usky pass sada rahay ga
  104,4,Hergiz nahi yeh to zaroor tor phor denay wali aag mein phenk diya jaeyga
  104,5,Aur tujhey kia maloom kay asi aag kiya hogi
  104,6,Woh Allah Taalaa ki sulgai hoi aag hogi
  104,7,Jo dilon per charhti chali jaey gi
  104,8,Who unn per her taraf say band ki hui hogi
  104,9,Bary bary satoonon mein
  105,1,Kia tu nay na dekha kay tery rab nay hathi walon kay sath kia kiya
  105,2,Kia unkay maker ko beykar nai kerdia
  105,3,Aur unper parindon kay jhond kay jhond bhej diey
  105,4,Jo unhein mitti or pather ki kankariyan mar rahy thy
  105,5,Pus unhein khaye huye bhoosy ki tarah kerdiya
  106,1,Quresh kay manoos kerney kay liye
  106,2,(yanni) unhen jary aur garmi kay safar say manoos kerney kay liey.(uskay shukriey main)
  106,3,Pus unhen chahey kay issi gher kay rab ki ibadat kerty rahen
  106,4,Jiss nay inhen bhook mein khana diya aur darr (aur khof) mein aman (o-aman) diya
  107,1,Kiya tu nay(ussay bhi)dekha jo (roz) jaza ko jhutlata hai
  107,2,yehi who hai jo yateem ko dhakkay deta hai
  107,3,Aur miskeen ko khilaney ki targeeb nahi deta
  107,4,Un namazion kay liey afsos(aur well nami jahanum ki jagah)hai
  107,5,Jo apni namaz say ghafil hain
  107,6,Jo riya kari kerty hein
  107,7,Aur baratnay ki chez roktay hain
  108,1,Yaqeenan hum nay tujhay (hoz)kusar (aur bhat kuch) diya hay
  108,2,Pus tu apney rab kay liey namz parh aur qurbani karo
  108,3,Yaqeenan tera dushman hi la-waris aur benam-o-nishan hai
  109,1,Aap khydijey kay aey kafiro
  109,2,Na mein ibadat kerta hun usski jiss kit um ibadat kerty ho
  109,3,Na tum ibadat kerney waly ho usski jisski mein ibadat kerta hon
  109,4,Aur na mein ibadat karon ga uski jisski tum ibadat kerty ho
  109,5,Aur na tum usski ibadat kerney waly hojisski mein ibadat ker raha hon
  109,6,Tumhary liey tumhara deen hai aur mery liey mera deen hai
  110,1,Jab Allah ji madad aur fatah ajaye
  110,2,Aur tu logon ko ALLAH kay deen mein jok dar jok aata dekh lay
  110,3,To apnay rabb ki tasbeeh karney lag hamd kay sath aur uss say maghfirat ki dua maang bey shak woh bara hi tauba qabool karney wala hai
  111,1,Abu Lahab ky dono hath toot gaye aur who (khud) halk ho gaya
  111,2,Na to uska maal usky kaam aya aur na uski kamai
  111,3,Who unqareeb bharkney waali aag mein jaey ga
  111,4,Aur uski biwi bhi(jaeygi)jo lakriyan dhonay waali hai
  111,5,usski gardan mein post khajoor ki bati hui rassi hogi
  112,1,Aap kehydijiye kay Woh ALLAH TaALA aik(hi)hai
  112,2,Allah bey niaz hai
  112,3,Na uss say koi paida hoa na who kisi say paida hoa
  112,4,Aur na koi uska humser hai
  113,1,Aap kehdijiye! Kay mein subha ky Rab ki panah mein aata hun
  113,2,Her uss cheez ky shar say jo uss nay paida ki hai
  113,3,Aur andheri raat ki tareki kay shar say jab uska andhera phel jaye
  113,4,Aur girah(laga ker inn)mein phonknay walon kay sher say(bhi)
  113,5,Aur hasad kerney waly ki burai say bhi jab wo hasad karey
  114,1,Aap kehdijiey!kay mein logo kay parwardigar ki panah mein ata hun
  114,2,Logon ky malik ki(aur)
  114,3,Logon ky maabood ki(Panah mein)
  114,4,Waswasa dalney waly pechy hut janey waly kay shar say
  114,5,Jo logon kay seenon mein waswasa daalta hai
  114,6,(Khua) woh jinn mein say ho ya insaan mein say